            <div class="title">
                Princess Elizabeth&#39;s And Duke Of Edinburgh&#39;s Annuities Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-01-20/debates/c9479da8-0ca2-4cff-aabb-9db0f134b189/OverseasResourcesDevelopmentBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
