<p class="">I must confess that I do not see that it has anything to do with the Bill before the House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-dc2467bc-d740-45d1-a104-481d81b8aefa" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
